{"data":[{"date":"09:10 19/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nga vs Ai C\u1eadp (1h00 ng\u00e0y 20/6): Salah, Salah v\u00e0... Salah","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/Nhan-dinh-Nga-vs-Ai-Cap-(1h00-ngay-206)-Salah,-Salah-va-Salah-hinh-anh-2.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Salah, Salah v\u00e0 Salah, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi t\u1ea7n su\u1ea5t l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1eefa Nga vs Ai C\u1eadp v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 Mohamed Salah.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Nga vs Ai C\u1eadp, ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn c\u00e1c t\u1edd b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp t\u1edbi Mohamed Salah. C\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i th\u00f4i, Salah \u0111ang l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp. \u1ede v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 ba World Cup 2018 khu v\u1ef1c ch\u00e2u Phi, Salah ghi \u0111\u1ebfn 5 trong s\u1ed1 8 b\u00e0n, gi\u00fap \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111\u1ebfn Nga h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nga vs Ai C\u1eadp (1h00 ng\u00e0y 206) Salah, Salah v\u00e0 Salah h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nga vs Ai C\u1eadp (1h00 ng\u00e0y 206) Salah, Salah v\u00e0 Salah h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/salah-11.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Mohamed Salah l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Nga vs Ai C\u1eadp.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp tin r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu Salah xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Uruguay, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u00edt nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu c\u1ea3nh tr\u1eafng tay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Hector Cuper kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Salah tr\u0103m ph\u1ea7n tr\u0103m s\u1ebd ra s\u00e2n tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, d\u00f9 r\u1eb1ng gi\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean ch\u1ee5p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3nh anh ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eb7c \u00e1o t\u1eadp. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c, \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp \u0111ang r\u01a1i v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf r\u1ea5t b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Saudi Arabia v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 5-0, trong khi Ai C\u1eadp thua Uruguay. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn \u0110T Nga c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i \u0111\u01b0a ra nhi\u1ec1u toan t\u00ednh h\u01a1n b\u1edfi ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Ai C\u1eadp bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft b\u1edfi ngay c\u1ea3 khi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a, h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng th\u1eadt \u0111\u1eadm Saudi Arabia r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ee3i Uruguay h\u1ea1 Nga \u1edf lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. C\u00f2n n\u1ebfu th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1eebng \u0111\u00f9a v\u1edbi Nga<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 c\u00f3 Mohamed Salah nh\u01b0ng \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nga tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Krestovsky. H\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, trong khi Nga ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m v\u1edbi Saudi Arabia.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nga vs Ai C\u1eadp (1h00 ng\u00e0y 206) Salah, Salah v\u00e0 Salah h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nga vs Ai C\u1eadp (1h00 ng\u00e0y 206) Salah, Salah v\u00e0 Salah h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/Nhan-dinh-Nga-vs-Ai-Cap-(1h00-ngay-206)-Salah,-Salah-va-Salah-hinh-anh-2.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Nga vs Ai C\u1eadp mang t\u00ednh quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u1edbn v\u1edbi su\u1ea5t \u0111i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSaudi Arabia qu\u00e1 ng\u00e2y th\u01a1 khi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Nga nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn l\u00e0 HLV Stanislav Cherchesov \u0111\u00e3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. V\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p Ai C\u1eadp, HLV Cherchesov t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Mohamed Salah ph\u1ea3i im ti\u1ebfng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Nga v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 Dzyuba, Smolov, Golovin hay Cheryshev - c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Villareal, ng\u01b0\u1eddi hi\u1ebfm hoi thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i trong \u0110T Nga l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Cherchesov nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng, sau \u0111\u00f3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng pha b\u00f3ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n. Dzyuba ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd k\u1ef9 nh\u1ea5t trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng, b\u1edfi \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o cao \u0111\u1ebfn 1m96 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 trung t\u00e2m b\u00f3ng h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u00f4ng tin l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng:</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nga:</strong> Dzagoev kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Ai C\u1eadp:</strong> T\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a Salah v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u1ea9n s\u1ed1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn:</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n g\u1eb7p nhau.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Li\u00ean X\u00f4, Nga ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng thua c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u Phi t\u1ea1i World Cup (th\u1eafng 2, h\u00f2a 1), bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 6-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Cameroon n\u0103m 1994, v\u1edbi Oleg Salenko ghi c\u1ea3 5 b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Ai C\u1eadp ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u \u00c2u t\u1ea1i World Cup (h\u00f2a 2, thua 2).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi Li\u00ean X\u00f4 tan r\u00e3, Nga ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u1edf 3 k\u1ef3 World Cup \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 (1994, 2002 v\u00e0 2014).&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* S\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0110T Nga ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 (5) nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n hai k\u1ef3 World Cup g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t h\u1ecd g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t l\u00e0 2014 (2) v\u00e0 2002 (4).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Nga vs Ai C\u1eadp (1h00 ng\u00e0y 20/6):</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nga (4-2-3-1):</strong> 1.Akinfeev - 2.M.Fernandes, 3.Kutepov, 4.Ignashevich, 18.Zhirkov - 8.Gazinskiy, 11.Zobnin - 19.Samedov, 17.Golovin, 6.Cheryshev - 10.Smolov</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Ai C\u1eadp (4-2-3-1):</strong> 23.El-Shenawy - 7.Fathy, 2.Gabr, 6.Hegazi, 13.Shafy - 8.Hamed, 17.Elneny - 10.Salah, 19.Said, 21.Trezeguet - 9.Mohsen</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1:</strong> Nga 2-2 Ai C\u1eadp<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Nga vs Ai Cap\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Nga vs Ai C\u1eadp\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/Nga-vs-Ai-Cap-(4-2-3-1-vs-4-2-3-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Nga vs Ai C\u1eadp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong> </strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ea1t (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"345","checkdouble":"188902"},{"date":"09:56 19/06","title":"Man City ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d 46,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/26/man-city-sap-co-jorginho-cua-napoli.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man City s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Jorginho c\u1ee7a Napoli. Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin c\u1ee7a Sky Sports, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chi 46,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Man City li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Jorginho l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1eeb l\u00e2u. \u0110\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y, ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00fd k\u1ebft. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111ang ch\u1edd 2 CLB \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng thu\u1eadn, bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh thanh to\u00e1n, ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed v\u00e0 l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng chi ti\u1ebft nh\u1ecf v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i Man City s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Jorginho.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man City s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Jorginho c\u1ee7a Napoli gi\u00e1 46,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Man City s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Jorginho c\u1ee7a Napoli gi\u00e1 46,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/26/man-city-sap-co-jorginho-cua-napoli.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Man City s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Jorginho c\u1ee7a Napoli gi\u00e1 46,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nJorginho m\u1edbi \u0111\u0103ng m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m \u1ea3nh tr\u00ean Instagram v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 c\u00f9ng gia \u0111\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Brazil. Anh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd bay t\u1edbi Manchester ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf khi n\u00e0o 2 CLB th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Jorginho \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 37 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho Napoli m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng bao g\u1ed3m 1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00ednh Man City t\u1ea1i Champions League h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 11.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nJorginho b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Verona tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Napoli n\u0103m 2014. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i nhanh ch\u00f3ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. K\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i\u1ec1u ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Jorginho gi\u00fap l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Napoli th\u00eam ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMan City c\u1ee7a HLV Pep Guardiola c\u0169ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Yaya Toure m\u1edbi ra \u0111i sau khi h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf v\u00e0 Jorginho l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o. Guardiola r\u1ea5t th\u00edch phong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Italia v\u00e0 tin anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Man City tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/soc-raheem-sterling-tu-choi-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-man-city-172-188324.html\">S\u1ed1c: Raheem Sterling t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/doi-bong-dau-tien-dam-phan-voi-yaya-toure-172-188052.html\">\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Yaya Toure</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/neymar-tha-thinh-man-city-pep-van-rat-tinh-don-172-187954.html\">Neymar \u201cth\u1ea3 th\u00ednh\u201d Man City, Pep v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t t\u1ec9nh \u0111\u00f2n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"344","checkdouble":"188904"},{"date":"10:42 19/06","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Fekir l\u1ea1i m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/nguoi-dai-dien-cua-fekir-lai-moi-goi-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>CSKA t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Golovin cho Juventus. D\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u Euro nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ea1i gia Italia v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang n\u1ed5i \u0111\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1m t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Golovin t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga khan hi\u1ebfm nh\u00e2n t\u00e0i, Aleksandr Golovin n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng. \u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, \u201cNh\u1eefng ch\u00fa g\u1ea5u\u201d \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng 5-0. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 n\u00e9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGolovin \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 2 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Nga t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c v\u00e0 cho th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf CSKA Moscow. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CSKA t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Golovin cho Juventus gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u Euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CSKA t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Golovin cho Juventus gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u Euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/cska-tu-choi-ban-golovin-cho-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Golovin t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o tuy\u1ec3n Nga</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n27 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho CSKA t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Nga, Golovin c\u00f3 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. \u1ede c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng, ki\u1ebfn thi\u1ebft, \u0111i b\u00f3ng cho t\u1edbi s\u00fat xa.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus mu\u1ed1n Golovin nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Golovin t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng gi\u00fap Nga th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u vang d\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Juventus t\u1eeb suy ngh\u0129 mang anh v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng. H\u1ecd g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u Euro t\u1edbi CSKA \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eaft x\u00edch m\u00ecnh mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Aleksandr Golovin\" title=\"tien ve Aleksandr Golovin\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/4/Juventus-muon-mua-Aleksandr-Golovin-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">CSKA t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Golovin cho Juventus</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c CSKA t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Golovin cho Juventus. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 thu v\u1ec1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 25 tri\u1ec7u Euro sau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i v\u1ed9i v\u00e0ng khi c\u00f3 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Golovin. M\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u00e1 gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c b\u00ean s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn CSKA \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n Juventus, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00e2u s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u01a1 b\u1eafp nh\u01b0 Sami Khedira, Blaise Matuidi hay Stefano Sturaro, Bianconeri mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 Miralem Pjanic trong kh\u00e2u s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o, \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ecd tin c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Rodrigo Bentancur ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Aleksandr Golovin tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhm-arsenal-nhan-hlv-unai-emery-hay-ngay-lap-tuc-mua-golovin-172-188557.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/nhm-arsenal-nhan-hlv-unai-emery-hay-ngay-lap-tuc-mua-golovin.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhm-arsenal-nhan-hlv-unai-emery-hay-ngay-lap-tuc-mua-golovin-172-188557.html\">NHM Arsenal nh\u1eafn HLV Unai Emery: H\u00e3y ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c mua Golovin</span><br>\r\n<span>Arsenal mua Aleksandr Golovin, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o NHM Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia.</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-nga-50-saudi-arabia-diem-10-cho-aleksandr-golovin-421-188547.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/du-am-nga-50-saudi-arabia-diem-10-cho-aleksandr-golovin.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-nga-50-saudi-arabia-diem-10-cho-aleksandr-golovin-421-188547.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Nga 5-0 Saudi Arabia: \u0110i\u1ec3m 10 cho Aleksandr Golovin</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u1eadn Nga vs Saudi Arabia b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Aleksandr Golovin \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5. Ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"343","checkdouble":"188906"},{"date":"10:57 19/06","title":"\"Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n C\u0110V Mexico \u0103n m\u1eebng t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ea5t\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/khong-the-co-chuyen-cdv-mexico-an-mung-tao-ra-dong-dat.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u C\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n qu\u1ed1c gia Mexico, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n c\u00e1c C\u0110V Mexico \u0103n m\u1eebng t\u1ea1o n\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \u0110\u1ee9c.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0110V Mexico t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ea5t<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/duc-vs-mexico-bang-f-463-188732.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">\u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico</span></span> k\u1ebft th\u00fac, C\u01a1 quan gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n Mexico (Simmsa)&nbsp; cho bi\u1ebft c\u00f3 hai c\u01a1n \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n \u1edf th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/sat-thu-lozano-noi-gi-sau-khi-choc-thung-luoi-dt-duc-421-188761.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">Hirving Lozano ghi b\u00e0n</span></span>. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00e0 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u00fap Mexico \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-0.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CDV Mexico an mung tao ra dong dat.\" title=\"C\u0110V Mexico \u0103n m\u1eebng t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ea5t.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/khong-the-co-chuyen-cdv-mexico-an-mung-tao-ra-dong-dat.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u0110V Mexico \u0103n m\u1eebng t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ea5t trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \u0110\u1ee9c.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 l\u1ebd b\u1edfi qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0103n m\u1eebng n\u00ean Simmsa ghi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hai c\u01a1n rung ch\u1ea5n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 2 \u0111\u1ed9 Richter. Vi\u1ec7c Mexico t\u1ea1o n\u00ean 2 c\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, c\u1ea3 theo ngh\u0129a \u0111en l\u1eabn ngh\u0129a b\u00f3ng khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Xyoli P\u00e9rez Campos, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u Trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n qu\u1ed1c gia Mexico (SSN) nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 tr\u00ean: &quot;C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi, ho\u1eb7c m\u1ed9t nh\u00f3m ng\u01b0\u1eddi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c nh\u1ea3y g\u1ea7n m\u00e1y \u0111o t\u1ea1o n\u00ean k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Con ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1ea3y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean rung ch\u1ea5n nh\u01b0ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ea5t&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">William Yeck, m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 kh\u1ea3o s\u00e1t \u0111\u1ecba t\u1ea7ng c\u1ee7a Hoa K\u1ef3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1: &quot;D\u0129 nhi\u00ean con ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra c\u00e1c c\u01a1n rung ch\u1ea5n nh\u01b0ng trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i kh\u00e1c. \u1ede \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 nh\u1ea3y \u0103n m\u1eebng th\u00ec kh\u00f3 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 v\u1eady&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo William Yeck, con ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean c\u00e1c c\u01a1n \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n nh\u00e2n t\u1ea1o ch\u1ec9 b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh l\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba t\u1ea7ng. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u1eefu h\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n nh\u01b0 khoan m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0o l\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5t khi th\u0103m d\u00f2 d\u1ea7u kh\u00ed, kho\u00e1ng s\u1ea3n,... ho\u1eb7c c\u00e1c v\u1ee5 th\u1eed h\u1ea1t nh\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cdv-mexico-tao-dong-dat-khi-mung-chien-tich-thang-duc-421-188800.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/cdv-mexico-tao-dong-dat-khi-mung-chien-tich-thang-duc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cdv-mexico-tao-dong-dat-khi-mung-chien-tich-thang-duc-421-188800.html\">C\u0110V Mexico t\u1ea1o ... \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ea5t khi m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch th\u1eafng \u0110\u1ee9c</span><br>\r\nC\u01a1 quan gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n Mexico (Simmsa) ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 hai c\u01a1n rung ch\u1ea5n \u1edf th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y, khi Lozano ghi b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"342","checkdouble":"188907"},{"date":"10:21 19/06","title":"Barca b\u1ecb sao Ajax n\u00f3i l\u1eddi cay \u0111\u1eafng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/de-jong-khong-muon-toi-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>De Jong kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Barca trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf cho Andres Iniesta trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>C\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c thay th\u1ebf Iniesta</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nK\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, Andres Iniesta \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay v\u1edbi Barcelona. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 34 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 x\u01b0a v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ea1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb. Iniesta kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n sang Vissel Kobe c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, m\u1ed9t CLB c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 v\u1edbi Barca.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia, h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u1eaft tay v\u00e0o t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. Trong danh s\u00e1ch n\u00e0y c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng bao g\u1ed3m t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Frenkie de Jong c\u1ee7a Ajax. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi tr\u00f4i qua ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 21 tu\u1ed5i b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin d\u00f9ng \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i 1 CLB c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 Lan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De Jong kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Barca trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"De Jong kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Barca trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/21/De-Jong-khong-muon-toi-Barca-trong-tuong-lai-gan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barca c\u1ea7n De Jong thay th\u1ebf Iniesta</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nDe Jong c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 22 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n (6 t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb) v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 7 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. Nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n c\u1ea3 trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng l\u1eabn d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb xa c\u1ee7a sao tr\u1ebb H\u00e0 Lan khi\u1ebfn Barca ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>B\u1ecb De Jong t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi t\u1edd Goal, De Jong kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Barca trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p Blaugrana h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n anh l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p h\u1eefu \u00edch cho hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Barca.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Frenkie de Jong cua Ajax\" title=\"Frenkie de Jong cua Ajax\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/de-jong-khong-muon-toi-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">De Jong kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Barca trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c<em>Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ecdc b\u00e1o T\u00e2y Ban Nha</em>\u201d, De Jong n\u00f3i. \u201c<em>\u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea5p thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i qu\u00e1 ch\u00fa t\u00e2m v\u00e0o n\u00f3. T\u00f4i giao n\u00f3 cho \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft li\u1ec7u \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u00f3 \u0111ang suy ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y hay kh\u00f4ng. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng.</em>\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i De Jong, Barca c\u0169ng \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Trong \u0111\u00f3, ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u l\u00e0 Ilkay Gundogan c\u1ee7a Man City d\u00f9 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-muon-trao-doi-nguoi-voi-tottenham-180-188303.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/barca-muon-trao-doi-nguoi-voi-tottenham.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-muon-trao-doi-nguoi-voi-tottenham-180-188303.html\">Barca mu\u1ed1n trao \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi Tottenham</span><br>\r\n<span>Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Christian Eriksen c\u1ee7a Tottenham, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n c\u1ed9ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Rafinha \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Spurs nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ivan-rakitic-noi-gi-truoc-vien-canh-neymar-cap-ben-real-madrid-180-188263.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/11/ivan-rakitic-noi-gi-truoc-vien-canh-neymar-cap-ben-real-madrid.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ivan-rakitic-noi-gi-truoc-vien-canh-neymar-cap-ben-real-madrid-180-188263.html\">Ivan Rakitic n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh Neymar c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real Madrid?</span><br>\r\n<span>Ivan Rakitic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 \u1edf Barca s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi PSG c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"341","checkdouble":"188908"},{"date":"10:42 19/06","title":"CSKA t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng World Cup cho \u0111\u1ea1i gia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/cska-tu-choi-ban-golovin-cho-juventus.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>CSKA t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Golovin cho Juventus. D\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u Euro nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ea1i gia Italia v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang n\u1ed5i \u0111\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1m t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Golovin t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga khan hi\u1ebfm nh\u00e2n t\u00e0i, Aleksandr Golovin n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng. \u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, \u201cNh\u1eefng ch\u00fa g\u1ea5u\u201d \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng 5-0. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 n\u00e9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGolovin \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 2 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Nga t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c v\u00e0 cho th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf CSKA Moscow. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CSKA t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Golovin cho Juventus gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u Euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CSKA t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Golovin cho Juventus gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u Euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/cska-tu-choi-ban-golovin-cho-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Golovin t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o tuy\u1ec3n Nga</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n27 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho CSKA t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Nga, Golovin c\u00f3 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. \u1ede c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng, ki\u1ebfn thi\u1ebft, \u0111i b\u00f3ng cho t\u1edbi s\u00fat xa.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus mu\u1ed1n Golovin nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Golovin t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng gi\u00fap Nga th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u vang d\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Juventus t\u1eeb suy ngh\u0129 mang anh v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng. H\u1ecd g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u Euro t\u1edbi CSKA \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eaft x\u00edch m\u00ecnh mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Aleksandr Golovin\" title=\"tien ve Aleksandr Golovin\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/4/Juventus-muon-mua-Aleksandr-Golovin-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">CSKA t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Golovin cho Juventus</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c CSKA t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Golovin cho Juventus. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 thu v\u1ec1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 25 tri\u1ec7u Euro sau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i v\u1ed9i v\u00e0ng khi c\u00f3 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Golovin. M\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u00e1 gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c b\u00ean s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn CSKA \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n Juventus, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00e2u s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u01a1 b\u1eafp nh\u01b0 Sami Khedira, Blaise Matuidi hay Stefano Sturaro, Bianconeri mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 Miralem Pjanic trong kh\u00e2u s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o, \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ecd tin c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Rodrigo Bentancur ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Aleksandr Golovin tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhm-arsenal-nhan-hlv-unai-emery-hay-ngay-lap-tuc-mua-golovin-172-188557.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/nhm-arsenal-nhan-hlv-unai-emery-hay-ngay-lap-tuc-mua-golovin.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhm-arsenal-nhan-hlv-unai-emery-hay-ngay-lap-tuc-mua-golovin-172-188557.html\">NHM Arsenal nh\u1eafn HLV Unai Emery: H\u00e3y ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c mua Golovin</span><br>\r\n<span>Arsenal mua Aleksandr Golovin, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o NHM Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia.</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-nga-50-saudi-arabia-diem-10-cho-aleksandr-golovin-421-188547.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/du-am-nga-50-saudi-arabia-diem-10-cho-aleksandr-golovin.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-nga-50-saudi-arabia-diem-10-cho-aleksandr-golovin-421-188547.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Nga 5-0 Saudi Arabia: \u0110i\u1ec3m 10 cho Aleksandr Golovin</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u1eadn Nga vs Saudi Arabia b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Aleksandr Golovin \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5. Ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"340","checkdouble":"188909"},{"date":"11:03 19/06","title":"Arsenal s\u1eafp c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 2 h\u00e8 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/arsenal-sap-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-bernd-leno.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c, Arsenal \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Bernd Leno c\u1ee7a Bayer Leverkusen.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n Bernd Leno</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Bernd Leno trong v\u00f2ng 48 gi\u1edd t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Bernd Leno trong v\u00f2ng 48 gi\u1edd t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/arsenal-sap-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-bernd-leno.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Bernd Leno</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Leno \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n 304 l\u1ea7n cho Bayer Leverkusen k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y n\u0103m 2011. Nh\u01b0ng theo tin \u0111\u1ed3n, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Arsenal tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng 2018/19.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed r\u01a1i v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. HLV Unai Emery \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Petr Cech ngay m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp theo. T\u1edd Bild kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Arsenal s\u1ebd ra m\u1eaft th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c trong v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u00e0y, Cech nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Th\u1ea7n g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi CH S\u00e9c nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd chia tay s\u00e2n Emirates \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t \u1edf phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cho \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nong-arsenal-chinh-thuc-don-tan-binh-dau-tien-duoi-thoi-emery-172-187828.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Stephan Lichtsteiner</span>. C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Juventus gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do. Anh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd k\u00fd v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi The Gunners.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trung v\u1ec7 Sokratis Papastathopoulos nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Emirates sau khi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t bu\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf. Cha c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Hy L\u1ea1p ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng Sokratis \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a Manchester United \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Arsenal.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201c\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb Man United. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd t\u1edbi th\u00e1ng 7 \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng\u201d, Charalambos Papastathopoulos chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean m\u1ed9t k\u00eanh radio c\u1ee7a Hy L\u1ea1p.<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cMan United c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi Dortmund. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Sokratis kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0ng con trai t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ecdn Arsenal\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal:<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/granit-xhaka-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-arsenal-172-188587.html\">Tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chieu-mo-torreira-tuong-lai-bat-dau-tu-hom-nay-172-188414.html\">Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Torreira: T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb h\u00f4m nay</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"339","checkdouble":"188910"},{"date":"11:44 19/06","title":"4 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 m\u00e0 \u0110T Anh c\u1ea7n kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/ba-van-de-ma-dt-anh-can-khac-phuc-sau-chien-thang-chat-vat-o-ngay-ra-quan.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n B\u1eafc Phi Tunisia. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn xa, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Gareth Southgate v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">1. S\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee5t m\u1ed9t \u2018b\u1ed9 \u00f3c\u2019 khu trung tuy\u1ebfn</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u1ea7n tham d\u1ef1 World Cup n\u00e0y, HLV Southgate \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh khi l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh gi\u00e0u t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u01a1 b\u1eafp v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c thay v\u00ec b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam nh\u1eefng n\u00e9t m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 Pogba, \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 Kroos, T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f3 Iniesta, Argentina c\u00f3 Messi, Brazil c\u00f3 Coutinho th\u00ec nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf \u0110T Anh. Sau khi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Jack Wilshere v\u00e0 Shelvey, Southgate \u0111ang \u0111\u1eb7t tr\u1ecdn ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ecdn d\u1eb9p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa nh\u01b0 Sterling, Alli v\u00e0 Lingard.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 m\u00e0 \u0110T Anh c\u1ea7n kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"4 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 m\u00e0 \u0110T Anh c\u1ea7n kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/4-van-de-ma-DT-Anh-can-khac-phuc-sau-chien-thang-truoc-Tunisia-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110T Anh \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee5t m\u1ed9t \u2018b\u1ed9 \u00f3c\u2019 khu trung tuy\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c th\u1eeba \u2018c\u00f4ng nh\u00e2n\u2019 thi\u1ebfu \u2018ngh\u1ec7 s\u0129\u2019 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i. Nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia m\u1edbi th\u1ea5y \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Southgate \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu \u0111i m\u1ed9t nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 c\u00f3 nh\u00e3n quan chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt s\u1eafc b\u00e9n c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7m nh\u1ecbp v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebft l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1eeb khu trung tuy\u1ebfn. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Loftus-Cheek l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, song li\u1ec7u Southgate c\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Cheek hay ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c trung th\u00e0nh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n?<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">2. V\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1eadn h\u00e0nh s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3-5-2 v\u1edbi tham v\u1ecdng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u1edd h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 h\u00f9ng h\u1eadu, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Gareth Southgate l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd qu\u00e1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh m\u00e0 b\u1ecf qu\u00ean m\u1ed9t nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i l\u00e0 Danny Rose. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Ashley Young, ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t, ng\u00f4i sao M.U \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf t\u1edbi l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 chung c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn Tam S\u01b0 su\u00fdt n\u1eefa ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Kane kh\u00f4ng h\u00f3a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng v\u1edbi pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec1m h\u00f3c v\u00e0o g\u00f3c xa khung th\u00e0nh \u1edf ph\u00fat 90+1.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 m\u00e0 \u0110T Anh c\u1ea7n kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"4 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 m\u00e0 \u0110T Anh c\u1ea7n kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/4-van-de-ma-DT-Anh-can-khac-phuc-sau-chien-thang-chat-vat-o-ngay-ra-quan-hinh-anh-2.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Young kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n trong tr\u1eadn Anh 2-1 Tunisia</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Danny Rose kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean cho Tottenham \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua nh\u01b0ng l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a anh l\u1ea1i \u1ea9n ch\u1ee9a s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m t\u1edbi t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng pha chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng. Ngay c\u1ea3 Fabian Delph c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n thay th\u1ebf th\u00edch h\u1ee3p b\u1edfi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh l\u00e0 \u0110T B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, h\u1ecd s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Tunisia \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n. Do \u0111\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T B\u1ec9, qua \u0111\u00f3 n\u00e9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a Brazil, Argentina, Germany v\u00e0 Portugal tr\u00ean con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">3. M\u1eb7t tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3-5-2<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi m\u00e0 s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u 3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t th\u1ecbnh h\u00e0nh t\u1ea1i Premier League th\u00ec HLV Southgate c\u0169ng b\u00ea nguy\u00ean chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt n\u00e0y l\u00ean \u0110T Anh. Li\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p h\u1ee3p l\u00ed v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3-5-2 t\u1eebng mang t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cho Conte trong n\u0103m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea v\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00edch h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd n\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 t\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00edch phong c\u00e1ch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd, ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ki\u1ec3u \u00dd.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gareth Southgate phat bieu ve tran Anh vs Tunisia\" title=\"Gareth Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Anh vs Tunisia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/gareth-southgate-ngoai-kane-cac-chan-sut-con-lai-cua-anh-qua-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>S\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3-5-2 c\u1ee7a Gareth Southgate ch\u01b0a ph\u00e1t huy s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u1edf tr\u1eadn Anh vs Tunisia</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kyler Walker\u00a0l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00f3 thi\u00ean h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u00e1 d\u00e3n bi\u00ean l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb b\u00f3 bu\u1ed9c \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m. Sterling nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 d\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 do di chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf anh l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng ph\u00eda sau ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane, trong khi Alli, nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt \u0111\u00f3ng vai s\u1ed1 10 \u1edf Tottenham s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng thay v\u00ec ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh s\u1ebd thay \u0111\u1ed5i chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ti\u1ebfp theo. Quay l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-4-2 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn v\u1edbi Tam s\u01b0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jamie Vardy s\u1ebd s\u00e1nh vai c\u00f9ng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Harry Kane tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng trong khi b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Sterling v\u00e0 Loftus-Cheek ch\u1eafn gi\u1eef hai h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh c\u00f2n Alli s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 10 quen thu\u1ed9c. N\u00f3 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n h\u1ecd s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">4. M\u00ecnh Kane l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Tunisia kh\u00f4ng \u2018chung m\u00e2m\u2019 v\u1ec1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9, \u0110T Anh su\u00fdt n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Harry Kane. Tuy nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u s\u1ebd ra sao n\u1ebfu Kane b\u1ecb \u2018b\u1eaft ch\u1ebft\u2019 nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi Messi hay Neymar.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda c\u1ee7a Raheem Sterling, Dele Alli\u00a0v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Jesse Lingard. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh HLV Southgate th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn sau tr\u1eadn: \u201c\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh l\u00fac n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 m\u00ecnh Harry Kane bi\u1ebft ghi b\u00e0n\u201d.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cu dup cua Harry Kane giup Anh gianh 3 diem truoc Tunisia\" title=\"C\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a Harry Kane gi\u00fap Anh gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/051014-kane.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>M\u00ecnh Kane l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng n\u1ebfu Anh \u0111i s\u00e2u t\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span>. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao Tam S\u01b0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec7n d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng khi m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u2018ch\u00e2n g\u1ed7\u2019 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed7i khi mang l\u00ean m\u00ecnh t\u1ea5m b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n tuy\u1ec3n Anh, Harry Kane v\u1eabn gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u \u201cTam S\u01b0\u201d, nh\u01b0ng \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Gareth Southgate ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u00eam qua n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfn xa \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng sau.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-tran-tunisia-12-anh-421-188878.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/diem-nhan-tran-tunisia-12-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-tran-tunisia-12-anh-421-188878.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n nh\u00ecn t\u1eeb chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ra qu\u00e2n v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 nh\u01b0ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0</span><br>\r\nTr\u00f2n tr\u0129nh 20 n\u0103m k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb France 98, Anh m\u1edbi l\u1ea1i th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n World Cup (m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1edd \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0) v\u00e0 tr\u00f9ng h\u1ee3p th\u00fa v\u1ecb thay, \u0111\u00f3 lu\u00f4n l\u00e0...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-tunisia-12-anh-harry-kane-xung-danh-doi-truong-421-188886.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/du-am-tunisia-12-anh-harry-kane-xung-danh-doi-truong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-tunisia-12-anh-harry-kane-xung-danh-doi-truong-421-188886.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Tunisia 1-2 Anh: Harry Kane! X\u1ee9ng danh \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng</span><br>\r\nHarry Kane t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap gi\u00fap Anh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Tunisia 2-1 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018, ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh t\u1ea1i sao anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-tunisia-12-anh-bang-g-world-cup-2018-461-188877.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/tong-hop-tunisia-12-anh-bang-g-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-tunisia-12-anh-bang-g-world-cup-2018-461-188877.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Tunisia 1-2 Anh (B\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nNh\u1edd c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a Harry Kane, Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n 2-1 ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia. Trong \u0111\u00f3 b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u1edf ph\u00fat 90+1.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"338","checkdouble":"188912"},{"date":"11:24 19/06","title":"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 ng\u00e0y 19/6: Ramos ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/ngay-hom-nay-196.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 World Cup 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (19/6). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi b\u00e1m s\u00e1t t\u1eebng chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh.</h2>(li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)<br>\r\n<h2>Ramos ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o Ronaldo</h2>\r\n\u1ede s\u00e2n t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u00f4m qua 18/6, Sergio Ramos c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh b\u1eaft ch\u01b0\u1edbc pha ng\u00e3 \u0103n v\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m tr\u00f2 vui cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u1ea7m ho\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha 3-3 \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. B\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ronaldo ghi cho Selecao tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11 m. Xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb pha v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Nacho t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho CR7 ng\u00e3 xu\u1ed1ng, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cho \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u1ea3 penalty. Nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ki\u1ebfn cho r\u1eb1ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \"\u0103n qu\u1ea3 l\u1eeba\" b\u1edfi pha \u0103n v\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo.<br>\r\n<h2><em>Xem clip\u00a0Ramos ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o\u00a0Ronaldo </em></h2>\r\n<em>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/19/Sergio_Ramos.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</em>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nTuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh c\u00e2u gi\u1edd</h2>\r\n\"Trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Australia, c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u00f4i l\u00e0m qu\u00e1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i quen v\u1edbi chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f4i l\u00fac, vi\u1ec7c c\u00e2u gi\u1edd gi\u00fap cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\", Hernandez chia s\u1ebb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede ph\u00fat 80 trong tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p th\u1eafng Australia, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Aziz Behich ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn 2-1. Trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Lucas Hernandez th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn lu\u00f4n c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh ki\u1ebfm c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \"di\u1ec5n k\u1ecbch\" \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e2u gi\u1edd.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/20180616T112132Z_2027355522_RC1E732D0650_RTRMADP_3_SOCCERWORLDCUPFRAAUS.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>Messi kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Maradona \u0111\u1ec3 m\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tay gi\u00e0nh World Cup</h2>\r\nC\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Argentina l\u00e0 Hernan Crespo b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 Messi: \"Messi kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 Maradona \u0111\u1ec3 m\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 m\u00ecnh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Messi c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i hi\u1ec3u. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n th\u00edch h\u1ee3p, nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i Barcelona v\u1eady. B\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng Messi s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi\".\r\n<h2>HLV tuy\u1ec3n Anh ch\u00ea ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ec7</h2>\r\nTrong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn, hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean Gareth Southgate nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Kane l\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y gi\u00fap \u201cTam s\u01b0\u201d chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng G.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/gareth-southgate-ngoai-kane-cac-chan-sut-con-lai-cua-anh-qua-toi-421-188882.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/gareth-southgate-ngoai-kane-cac-chan-sut-con-lai-cua-anh-qua-toi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/gareth-southgate-ngoai-kane-cac-chan-sut-con-lai-cua-anh-qua-toi-421-188882.html\">Gareth Southgate: Ngo\u00e0i Kane, c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Anh qu\u00e1 t\u1ed3i</span><br>\r\n<span>Gareth Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Tunisia vs Anh, trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 HLV 47 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi duy nh\u1ea5t Harry Kane.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chia tay World Cup v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\nLi\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Iran cho bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 y t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y nhanh ch\u00f3ng ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh ki\u1ec3m tra v\u00e0 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn 4 tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u01a1 c\u1ee7a Cheshmi b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u00f2n m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean Carlos Queiroz, b\u1edfi Cheshmi l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111a n\u0103ng, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"337","checkdouble":"188913"},{"date":"11:37 19/06","title":"L\u1ecbch truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay 19/6","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/19/lich-truyen-hinh-phat-song-truc-tiep-world-cup-2018-196.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u00ean trang b\u00e1o b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Fifa World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay 19/6 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0i VTV v\u00e0 HTV v\u00e0 tr\u00ean c\u00e1c h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng internet</h2><div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/19/trai-bong.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<br />\r\nMohamed Salah c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi h\u00f4m nay \u0111ang tr\u00f4ng ch\u1edd tin t\u1ee9c li\u1ec7u anh c\u00f3 ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u00eam nay, khi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ai C\u1eadp g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0110T Nga c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eb1ng 5-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u1ea2 R\u1eadp X\u00ea \u00dat, \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nC\u01a1 h\u1ed9i g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong v\u00f2ng 1/16 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00eam nay. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Nga th\u00ec \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean x\u00e1ch va ly v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ni\u1ec1m hi v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed5 d\u1ed3n n\u00ean vai Mohamed Salah. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra t\u1ed1i nay l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea3ng H s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra, \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y Colombia l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i <br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ecbch truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay 196 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ecbch truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay 196 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/lich-truyen-hinh-phat-song-world-cup-2018-19-6.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Ai C\u1eadp kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh 100% Mohamed Salah s\u1ebd ra s\u00e2n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n   