ght:15.0pt;overflow:hidden;padding-bottom:2px;&#10;  padding-top:2px\" data-sheets-value=\"{\" lan=\"\" vs=\"\">Ba   Lan vs Senegal</td>\r\n            <td style=\"overflow:hidden;padding-bottom:2px;padding-top:2px\" data-sheets-value=\"{\">19/06   22h00</td>\r\n            <td style=\"overflow:hidden;padding-bottom:2px;padding-top:2px\" data-sheets-value=\"{\" vtv6=\"\" htv=\"\">VTV   6, VTV6 HD, HTV1, HTV TT, HTV4, , HTV9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr height=\"20\" style=\"height:15.0pt\">\r\n            <td height=\"20\" style=\"height:15.0pt;overflow:hidden;padding-bottom:2px;&#10;  padding-top:2px\" data-sheets-value=\"{\" vs=\"\" ai=\"\">Nga   vs Ai C\u1eadp</td>\r\n            <td style=\"overflow:hidden;padding-bottom:2px;padding-top:2px\" data-sheets-value=\"{\">20/06   01h00</td>\r\n            <td style=\"overflow:hidden;padding-bottom:2px;padding-top:2px\" data-sheets-value=\"{\" vtv3=\"\" htv=\"\" htv4=\"\">VTV   3, VTV3 HD, HTV1, HTV TT, HTV4 , HTV9, HTV7</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"336","checkdouble":"188914"},{"date":"07:26 19/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Colombia vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (19h00 ng\u00e0y 19/6): Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/Colombia-vs-Nhat.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho CLB Tottenham Son Heung-min \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng ra nh\u1eadn tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ec1 minh sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua 18/6.</h2><h2>Son Heung-min nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i v\u1ec1 m\u00ecnh sau tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 1-0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Son Heung-min n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Son Heung-min n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/chan-sut-son-heungmin-noi-gi-sau-tran-ra-quan-that-bai-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>V\u1ebb m\u1eb7t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Son Heung-min khi \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Son Heung-min v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 chi\u1ec1u 18/6. \u1ede m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n, d\u00f9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u00ecm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e0nh b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thua 0-1 chi\u1ec1u qua \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t h\u1eb9p, khi m\u00e0 hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Mexico \u0111\u1ec1u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm. Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Son Heung-min \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n xin l\u1ed7i c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i v\u00ec n\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y&rdquo;, Son Heung-min n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng khi v\u1ec1 \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Son Heung-min r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00ecnh khi anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Spurs c\u0169ng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y: &ldquo;Khi t\u00f4i \u1edf Tottenham, m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t.&nbsp;Khi t\u00f4i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n \u1edf Tottenham&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> g\u1eb7p Mexico v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 23.6 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Rostov Arena (Rostov). \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quan tr\u1ecdng m\u00e0 Son Heung-min v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-yeu-to-khien-bong-da-han-quoc-khong-the-tao-dia-chan-tai-world-cup-2018-421-188894.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/3-yeu-to-khien-bong-da-han-quoc-khong-the-tao-dia-chan-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-yeu-to-khien-bong-da-han-quoc-khong-the-tao-dia-chan-tai-world-cup-2018-421-188894.html\">3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u00e0o trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00f3i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-thuy-dien-10-han-quoc-bang-f-world-cup-2018-461-188852.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/tong-hop-thuy-dien-10-han-quoc-bang-f-world-cup-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-thuy-dien-10-han-quoc-bang-f-world-cup-2018-461-188852.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 1-0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c (B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nNh\u1edd s\u1ef1 can thi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i video (VAR), Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 1-0 t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"335","checkdouble":"188891"},{"date":"07:31 19/06","title":"Sao H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2 sau tr\u1eadn thua S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/sao-ha-noi-doi-mat-an-treo-gio-sau-tran-thua-sai-gon-fc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF m\u1ed5 b\u0103ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 14 V-League, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110\u00e0o Duy Kh\u00e1nh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2 nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Oseni hay trung v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a HAGL.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110\u00e0o Duy Kh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2 sau tr\u1eadn S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 5-2 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110\u00e0o Duy Kh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2 sau tr\u1eadn thua S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110\u00e0o Duy Kh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2 sau tr\u1eadn thua S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/Dao-Duy-Khanh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110\u00e0o Duy Kh\u00e1nh gi\u1eadt c\u00f9i ch\u1ecf v\u00e0o v\u00f9ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n v\u00e0o Nam \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC. V\u00e0 trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y x\u1ea5u tr\u1eddi, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1eeba c\u00f3 m\u1ea1ch 13 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t S\u00e0i G\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 2-5 chung cu\u1ed9c kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 khi\u1ebfn H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i b\u1ecb ng\u1eaft m\u1ea1ch 13 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i m\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110\u00e0o Duy Kh\u00e1nh khi m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 v\u00ec l\u1ed7i \u0111\u00e1nh ngu\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pha b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 75, trong l\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111ang d\u1eabn 4-2. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 Duy Kh\u00e1nh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng gi\u1eadt c\u00f9i ch\u1ecf v\u00e0o c\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a Da Sylva trong l\u00fac ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n m\u1ed9t pha ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhanh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i k\u00edn c\u1ee7a Duy Kh\u00e1nh d\u0129 nhi\u00ean qua m\u1eaft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Nguy\u1ec5n Minh Thu\u1eadn&nbsp;song h\u00e0nh vi c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 98 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi \u1ed1ng k\u00ednh truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, \u0110\u00e0o Duy Kh\u00e1nh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t ngu\u1ed9i t\u1eeb Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n g\u1eedi ki\u1ebfn ngh\u1ecb l\u00ean ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u1ed5 b\u0103ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay, VFF l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t nghi\u00eam v\u1edbi c\u00e1c l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, trung v\u1ec7 V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a HAGL \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i treo gi\u00f2 3 tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi l\u1ed7i \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Douglas Tardin, trong khi Oseni c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u hai tr\u1eadn c\u0169ng v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi \u0111\u00e1nh ngu\u1ed9i v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ph\u1ea1m M\u1ea1nh H\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a&nbsp;SLNA.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/du-am-sai-gon-52-ha-noi-su-that-nao-sau-tam-man-nhung-168-188784.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/du-am-sai-gon-52-ha-noi-su-that-nao-sau-tam-man-nhung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/du-am-sai-gon-52-ha-noi-su-that-nao-sau-tam-man-nhung-168-188784.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 5-2 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i: S\u1ef1 th\u1eadt n\u00e0o sau t\u1ea5m m\u00e0n nhung?</span><br>\r\nTrong c\u01a1n m\u01b0a n\u1eb7ng h\u1ea1t t\u1ea1i Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t chi\u1ec1u qua, CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd th\u00fac th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang x\u1ebfp \u00e1p ch\u00f3t tr\u00ean BXH l\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/vleague/ha-noi-thua-dam-sai-gon-bat-dau-co-che-xin-cho-291-188777.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/ha-noi-thua-dam-sai-gon-bat-dau-co-che-xin-cho.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/vleague/ha-noi-thua-dam-sai-gon-bat-dau-co-che-xin-cho-291-188777.html\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thua \u0111\u1eadm S\u00e0i G\u00f2n: B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf xin - cho?</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi li\u00ean t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf xin - cho v\u1ed1n v\u1eabn t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i \u1edf V-League, b\u1edfi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u nghi v\u1ea5n quanh tr\u1eadn thua...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-vong-14-vleague-2018-372-188725.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-vong-14-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-vong-14-vleague-2018-372-188725.html\">S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 5-2 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i (KT): Da Sylva l\u1eadp poker, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0110\u00f4 thua tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i V-League 2018</span><br>\r\nB\u1ed1n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Da Sylva \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap cho S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC gi\u00e0nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng 5-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. Thua tr\u1eadn, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t m\u1ea1ch b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf con s\u1ed1 13.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-family: Antenna-Regular, serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"334","checkdouble":"188892"},{"date":"07:52 19/06","title":"3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/3-yeu-to-khien-bong-da-han-quoc-khong-the-tao-dia-chan-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u00e0o trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00f3i t\u1edbi sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n</h2>\r\n<h2><o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi t\u00e2m l\u00fd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u khi m\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Mexico \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea9y &lsquo;nh\u1eefng c\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng&rsquo; v\u00e0o th\u1ebf bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng 2 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i m\u1edbi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec th\u1ebf, n\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t trong hai \u0111\u1ed9i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, c\u00f3 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 ch\u00fat l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tranh t\u00e0i v\u1edbi hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng. L\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00f3t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, BHL \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ngay sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i khai cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong kho\u1ea3ng 10 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn, ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n l\u00e0m kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng pha h\u00e3m th\u00e0nh tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a HLV Janne Andersson \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y v\u00ec sao h\u1ecd x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, khi s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1eebng khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Italia ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong tr\u1eadn play-off gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/3-yeu-to-khien-DT-Han-Quoc-khong-the-tao-dia-chan-tai-World-Cup-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ec9 huy b\u1edfi &lsquo;th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh&rsquo; Andreas Granqvist n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i, &lsquo;c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn binh Viking&rsquo; thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt, t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 kh\u00f4n ngoan tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 khao kh\u00e1t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. H\u1ecd b\u00edt ch\u1eb7t m\u1ecdi l\u1ed7 h\u1ed5ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Olsen v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch n\u00e0o \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat th\u0103m d\u00f2 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao h\u01a1n \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfm l\u0129nh th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. C\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a HLV Janne Andersson t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c c\u00e1c mi\u1ebfng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng kh\u00e1 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng. Ph\u00fat 20, su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb B\u1eafc \u00c2u n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Marcus Berg kh\u00f4ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang ch\u00e2n th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n li\u00ean t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y s\u1ee9c \u00e9p l\u00ean khung th\u00e0nh H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c bu\u1ed9c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Cho Hyun-woo ph\u1ea3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u1ed5 t\u00e0i c\u1ee9u thua. Sau th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Ibrahimovic, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat t\u1ea7m c\u1ee1, tuy nhi\u00ean nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c khi\u1ebfn H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 d\u00e2ng cao \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm b\u00e0n g\u1ee1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c 1-0, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. C\u00f2n v\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 g\u1eb7p Mexico, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n v\u1eeba \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00f4m Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt v\u1eeba qua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>VAR l\u00e0m h\u1ea1i &lsquo;nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn binh Taegeuk&rsquo;<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i video VAR (video assistant referee) \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c FIFA mang t\u1edbi k\u1ef3 World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y v\u1edbi hy v\u1ecdng vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 xem l\u1ea1i b\u0103ng h\u00ecnh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c nh\u1ea5t, nh\u1eb1m mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p &ndash; \u00dac v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m penalty thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 \u00e1 qu\u00e2n EURO 2016. V\u00e0 t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 1-0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, VAR l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 d\u1ecbp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng. Sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c truy c\u1ea3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Kim chi \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh &lsquo;n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n&rsquo; ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/11_QEFD.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 1-0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd kh\u00e1c n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3&nbsp;VAR</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tranh c\u00e3i n\u1ed5 ra \u1edf ph\u00fat 63 khi Min Woo va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi Claesson trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. Ban \u0111\u1ea7u, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Aguilar Joel kh\u00f4ng th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t. Tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ee9c \u00e9p c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, v\u1ecb vua \u00e1o \u0111en ng\u01b0\u1eddi El Salvador \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1edd t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap c\u1ee7a VAR. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 sau khi xem r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 b\u0103ng quay ch\u1eadm, \u00f4ng Aguilar Joel \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cho Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. Tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11 m\u00e9t, &quot;l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng&quot; Granqvist \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4n ngoan \u0111\u00e1nh l\u1eeba th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Cho Hyun-woo, ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 cho Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, gi\u00fap h\u1ecd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng sau 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p may khi ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 VAR th\u00ec h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 b\u1ebf t\u1eafc c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n m\u1edbi th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Shin Tae-yong r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 vai tr\u00f2 l\u00e0m b\u00f3ng - playmaker khu trung tuy\u1ebfn. V\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c l\u1eabn t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 thua k\u00e9m Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, song h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi nay, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng, nh\u1eefng pha d\u1ed1c b\u00f3ng xu\u1ed1ng bi\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c trung phong cao l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd t\u00ecm c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ea7u. L\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1eafp, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i, thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ea7u \u00f3c, t\u01b0 duy gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/1_YPEA.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng 'g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3' Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1edfi v\u1eady,khi g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0ng \u1edf m\u1ed9t c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 cao h\u01a1n nh\u01b0 \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n th\u00ec H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1. D\u00f9 s\u1edf h\u1eefu d\u00e0n sao \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u01b0 Son Heung-min, Ki Sung Yong, Lee Chung Yong hay Ji Dong Won nh\u01b0ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u1ea1i thi\u1ebfu m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c c\u00f3 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean, HLV Shin Tae-yong \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5t tay khi tung ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 gi\u00e0u k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 &lsquo;Messi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c&rsquo; Lee Seung-woo v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. Tuy nhi\u00ean t\u00e0i n\u0103ng n\u0103m nay m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 20 tu\u1ed5i d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tho\u00e1t hi\u1ec3m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c thua Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft c\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi c\u00e1c C\u0110V b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-nong-world-cup-c469-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup </span>n\u0103m nay, khi m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Mexico \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-thuy-dien-10-han-quoc-bang-f-world-cup-2018-461-188852.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/tong-hop-thuy-dien-10-han-quoc-bang-f-world-cup-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-thuy-dien-10-han-quoc-bang-f-world-cup-2018-461-188852.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 1-0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c (B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nNh\u1edd s\u1ef1 can thi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i video (VAR), Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 1-0 t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thong-ke-khong-the-bo-qua-tran-thuy-dien-10-han-quoc-421-188854.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/5-diem-nhan-Thuy-Dien-vs-Han-Quoc-bang-F-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thong-ke-khong-the-bo-qua-tran-thuy-dien-10-han-quoc-421-188854.html\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 1-0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c b\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m c\u1ee7a Granqvist. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/5-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-thuy-dien-10-han-quoc-421-188857.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/5-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-thuy-dien-10-han-quoc.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/5-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-thuy-dien-10-han-quoc-421-188857.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 1-0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-0, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"333","checkdouble":"188894"},{"date":"08:11 19/06","title":"Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Son Heung-min n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/chan-sut-son-heungmin-noi-gi-sau-tran-ra-quan-that-bai-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho CLB Tottenham Son Heung-min \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng ra nh\u1eadn tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ec1 minh sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua 18/6.</h2><h2>Son Heung-min nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i v\u1ec1 m\u00ecnh sau tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 1-0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Son Heung-min n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Son Heung-min n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/chan-sut-son-heungmin-noi-gi-sau-tran-ra-quan-that-bai-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>V\u1ebb m\u1eb7t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Son Heung-min khi \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Son Heung-min v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 chi\u1ec1u 18/6. \u1ede m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n, d\u00f9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u00ecm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e0nh b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thua 0-1 chi\u1ec1u qua \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t h\u1eb9p, khi m\u00e0 hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Mexico \u0111\u1ec1u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm. Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Son Heung-min \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n xin l\u1ed7i c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i v\u00ec n\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y&rdquo;, Son Heung-min n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng khi v\u1ec1 \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Son Heung-min r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00ecnh khi anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Spurs c\u0169ng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y: &ldquo;Khi t\u00f4i \u1edf Tottenham, m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t.&nbsp;Khi t\u00f4i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n \u1edf Tottenham&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> g\u1eb7p Mexico v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 23.6 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Rostov Arena (Rostov). \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quan tr\u1ecdng m\u00e0 Son Heung-min v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-yeu-to-khien-bong-da-han-quoc-khong-the-tao-dia-chan-tai-world-cup-2018-421-188894.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/3-yeu-to-khien-bong-da-han-quoc-khong-the-tao-dia-chan-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-yeu-to-khien-bong-da-han-quoc-khong-the-tao-dia-chan-tai-world-cup-2018-421-188894.html\">3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u00e0o trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00f3i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-thuy-dien-10-han-quoc-bang-f-world-cup-2018-461-188852.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/tong-hop-thuy-dien-10-han-quoc-bang-f-world-cup-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-thuy-dien-10-han-quoc-bang-f-world-cup-2018-461-188852.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 1-0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c (B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nNh\u1edd s\u1ef1 can thi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i video (VAR), Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 1-0 t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"332","checkdouble":"188895"},{"date":"08:31 19/06","title":"HLV \u0110T Nga t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi Ai C\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/6/13/hlv-dt-nga-tu-tin-doi-pho-voi-ai-cap.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u then ch\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp, HLV \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga, Stanislav Cherchesov \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra t\u1ef1 tin trong vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah.</h2><h2>HLV \u0110T Nga t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi Ai C\u1eadp</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Nga s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i World Cup n\u0103m nay g\u1eb7p \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u then ch\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 b\u1edfi n\u1ebfu gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, n\u00f3 c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Ai C\u1eadp b\u1edfi c\u00e1c v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb ch\u00e2u Phi c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh ba \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u tay \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp sau tr\u1eadn thua Uruguay.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV \u0110T Nga t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi Ai C\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV \u0110T Nga t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi Ai C\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/HLV-DT-Nga-tu-tin-doi-pho-voi-Ai-Cap-cua-Mohamed-Salah-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga t\u1ef1 tin trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3&nbsp;v\u1edbi Ai C\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebd trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u qua 18/6, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0, \u00f4ng Stanislav Cherchesov \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;\u0110T Nga \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ecdi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 Ai C\u1eadp v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u0129 nhi\u00ean Ai C\u1eadp v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao nh\u01b0 Mohamed Salah trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m ri\u00eang c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, \u0110T Nga t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ai C\u1eadp. V\u00e0 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y mai&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi Salah, HLV tuy\u1ec3n Nga, Cherchesov tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi: ''T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec, ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. T\u00f4i tin v\u00e0o c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng v\u00e0 s\u1ebd l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y''.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ra v\u1ec1, \u00f4ng Cherchesov c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i v\u00e0o c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 54 tu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i: &ldquo;T\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o \u0110T Nga, tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng Nga \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa \u0110T Nga vs Ai C\u1eadp s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra l\u00fac 1h00 ng\u00e0y 20/6, theo gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn. K\u00ednh m\u1eddi qu\u00fd v\u1ecb v\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n quan t\u00e2m theo d\u00f5i./.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dinh-chan-thuong-gan-khoeo-alan-dzagoev-nghi-het-vong-bang-421-188749.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/Dinh-chan-thuong-gan-khoeo,-Alan-Dzagoev-nghi-het-vong-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dinh-chan-thuong-gan-khoeo-alan-dzagoev-nghi-het-vong-bang-421-188749.html\">\u0110T Nga nh\u1eadn hung tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Ai C\u1eadp t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup</span><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb Sky Sports, g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i \u0110T Nga, Alan Dzagoev s\u1ebd ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i \u1edf tr\u1eadn khai m\u1ea1c...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-ai-cap-vs-uruguay-salah-buon-suarez-nao-co-vui-gi-421-188597.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/du-am-ai-cap-vs-uruguay-salah-buon-suarez-nao-co-vui-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-ai-cap-vs-uruguay-salah-buon-suarez-nao-co-vui-gi-421-188597.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Ai C\u1eadp 0-1 Uruguay: Salah bu\u1ed3n, Suarez n\u00e0o c\u00f3 vui g\u00ec</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0 \u00e2m Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y nu\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc c\u1ee7a hai ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Trong khi Salah bu\u1ed3n b\u00e3 nh\u00ecn \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u1ec3 thua v\u00e0o ph\u00fat...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"331","checkdouble":"188896"}]}